 that don't disqualify it.\n\nMy rationale: \"The raw NOTAM text confirms a broad closure of western Tehran FIR airports with specific exceptions that operate under limited daylight hours and fresh approval requirements, which meets the rule's definition of a major closure with permissible limited exceptions.\"","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ea3bac8bacea443aaf81f5","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The raw NOTAM text confirms a broad closure of western Tehran FIR with"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The raw NOTAM text confirms a broad closure of western Tehran FIR with","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782830086931,"responseId":"gen-1782830087-5naWeFrqnDM1B7yuCc3l","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to review the case details and the submitted evidence to make a decision. Let's identify the key evidence and the rule.\n\nThe case is about whether Iran initiated a major non-weather closure of its airspace by May 24, 2026 by 11:59 PM ET.\n\nThe rule (PX-1/DX-Rule) states that a \"major closure\" means:\n- A broad closure, cancellation, or suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving in, and departing from Iranian airspace or a major Iranian airspace region, or\n- A non-weather complete suspension of commercial arrivals and departures affecting at least two listed airports (IKA, THR, MHD, SYZ, IFN), and\n- With the understanding that limited exceptions to a broad closure (like per-flight approvals) don't disqu