ad closure in the western Tehran FIR region with permissible exceptions, meeting the rule's criteria. The rationale needs to be concise: mention the raw NOTAM confirming the closure with specific exceptions that fit under allowed limited exceptions.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning","type":"thinking"},{"text":"","type":"text"}],"model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1782830095-7BTab7rPHwrQU3N3EQ2g","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509","role":"assistant","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782830095287,"usage":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":19120,"output":559,"totalTokens":19679}},"type":"message_update"}
